Artists.name: PVRIS
Artists.about: PVRIS is an American rock band from Lowell, Massachusetts formed by members Lynn Gunn, Alex Babinski, and Brian MacDonald. The band formed originally under the name Paris but later changed it to PVRIS in the summer of 2013 citing legal reasons.

Artists.name: Seether
Artists.about: Seether are a South African rock band founded in May 1999 in Pretoria, Gauteng, South Africa.

Artists.name: Rainbow Kitten Surprise
Artists.about: Rainbow Kitten Surprise is an alternative/indie rock band from Boone, NC

Artists.name: First Aid Kit
Artists.about: First Aid Kit is a Swedish folk duo that consists of the sisters Klara and Johanna Sderberg. When performing live, the duo are accompanied by a drummer, a pedal steel guitarist and recently a keyboard player.

Artists.name: The Head and the Heart
Artists.about: The Head and the Heart is an American indie folk band. They were formed in the summer of 2009 by Josiah Johnson and Jonathan Russell. The band also includes Charity Rose Thielen, Chris Zasche, Kenny Hensley, and Tyler Williams.
